data.description: William II floor plan in the new phase of Wando Woodlands offering 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths plus a media room. Presidential trim package with heavy moldings throughout the 1st floor and ORB fixtures throughout entire home. Large oversized master suite can be found on the 1st floor with a massive walk-in closet. Kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances, hardwood flooring, and an island. Four large bedrooms upstairs along with a Jack & Jill bathroom, 1 additional bath, and a media room. Front elevation of home will be total brick/stone with a front porch. Home currently under construction. Photos are stock photos and some options may not reflect list price.
